 Bosa]] || colspan=\"2\" | {{abbr|LDE|Defensive End}} || [[Tanoh Kpassagnon]]\n|-\n| [[Sheldon Day]] || colspan=\"2\" | {{abbr|LDT|Defensive Tackle}} || [[Chris Jones (defensive tackle, born 1994)|Chris Jones]]\n|-\n| [[DeForest Buckner]] || colspan=\"2\" | RDT || [[Derrick Nnadi]]\n|-\n| [[Arik Armstead]] || colspan=\"2\" | RDE || [[Frank Clark (American football)|Frank Clark]]\n|-\n| | [[Fred Warner (American football)|Fred Warner]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | MIKE || style=\"text-align:center;\" | LB || [[Anthony Hitchens]]\n|-\n| | [[Dre Greenlaw]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | WILL || style=\"text-align:center;\" | LB || [[Damien Wilson]]\n|-\n| | [[Richard Sherman (American football)|Richard Sherman]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | LCB || style=\"text-align:center;\" | LB || [[Reggie Ragland]]\n|-\n| | [[Emmanuel Moseley]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | RCB || style=\"text-align:center;\" | LCB || [[Charvarius Ward]]\n|-\n| | [[K'Waun Williams]] || style=\"text-align:center;\" | NB || style=\"text-align:center;\" | RCB || [[Bashaud Breeland]]\n|-\n| [[Jimmie Ward]] || colspan=\"2\" | FS || [[Daniel Sorensen]]\n|-\n| [[Jaquiski Tartt]] || colspan=\"2\" | SS || [[Tyrann Mathieu]]\n|}\n\n==Officials==\n\nSuper Bowl LIV had seven officials. The numbers in parentheses below indicate their uniform numbers.<ref name=\"officiatingcrew\" /><ref>{{cite web|last=Filipe|first=Cameron|title=Bill Vinovich is the referee for Super Bowl LIV|url=http://www.footballzebras.com/2020/01/bill-vinovich-is-the-referee-for-super-bowl-liv/|website=FootballZebras.com|date=January 15, 2020|access-date=January 22, 2020}}</ref>\n*Referee: [[Bill Vinovich]] (52)\n*Umpire: Barry Anderson (20)\n*Down judge: Kent Payne (79)\n*Line judge: Carl Johnson (101)\n*Field judge: Michael Banks (72)\n*Side judge: Boris Cheek (41)\n*Back judge: Greg Steed (12)\n*Replay official: Mike Chase\n*Replay assistant: Marv LeBlanc\n*Alternates:\n**Referee: John Hussey (35)\n**Umpire: Bryan Neale (11)\n**Short wing: Tom Stephan (68)\n**Deep wing: Jimmy Buchanan (86)\n**Back judge: Greg Wilson (119)\n\n==References==\n\n{{reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==External links==\n\n{{Sisterlinks|d=Q20204363|c=Category:Super Bowl LIV|b=no|v=no|voy=no|m=no|mw=no|wikt=no|s=no|species=no|q=no|n=no}}\n*{{YouTube|id=jQ1l5zenaKY|title=Super Bowl LIV: NFL Full Game}}\n*{{URL|https://www.miamisb2020.com|Official host committee website}}\n*{{URL|https://www.foxsports.com/nfl/super-bowl-2020|Official broadcast website}}\n\n{{Super Bowl}}\n{{Super Bowl LIV}}\n{{Kansas City Chiefs}}\n{{San Francisco 49ers}}\n{{2019 NFL season by team}}\n{{NFLC-SuperBowl}}\n{{NFL on Fox}}\n{{authority control}}\n{{Portalbar|American football|Florida}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Super Bowl 54}}\n[[Category:Super Bowl|Super Bowl 054]]\n[[Category:2019 National Football League season]]\n[[Category:2020 in American football]]\n[[Category:2020 in sports in Florida]]\n[[Category:2020s in Miami]]\n[[Category:American football in Florida]]\n[[Category:Kansas City Chiefs postseason]]\n[[Category:San Francisco 49ers postseason]]\n[[Category:Sports competitions in Florida]]\n[[Category:2020 in American television]]\n[[Category:February 2020 sports events in the United States]]\n[[Category:Sports competitions in Miami Gardens, Florida]]\n", "name_user": "Games of the world", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Super_Bowl_LIV"}
